    <h2>A structural market, not a seasonal one</h2>
    <p class="partner-section__lead">Exertional heat stroke is not a trend. The convergence of global warming, tightening regulation, and the growth of endurance sports is creating sustained demand across every market you already serve.</p>

    <div class="partner-stats">

