      <div class="partner-stat">
        <div class="partner-stat__figure">Regulatory</div>
        <div class="partner-stat__label">growing obligation</div>
        <p>France, the United Kingdom, the European Union, Gulf countries: legal obligations around heat risk in the workplace and at sporting events are tightening. Every new regulation opens an equipment market. Sources: Decree 2025-482 (FR), HSE Heat Stress (UK), ISO 7933 guidelines.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

